item.description:
Grachi: La Vida es Maravillosamente Mágica (Life is Wonderfully Magical) is the first official soundtrack of the Nickelodeon's hit teen series Grachi. The album was released on June 7, 2011 in Mexico, distributed by EMI Music.
The original tracklist contains like 10 more songs from various latin popstars who made songs specifically about the TV series but were not included on the digital release, only these four songs sang by the original cast were released digitally on an EP which is not available for streaming anymore, luckily i downloaded it and now i share it with you my friends
